{"tid":1292492,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大陸旅客接反送中傳單　「想了解香港發生甚麼事」","createTime":"2019-07-07T10:50:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-08T17:10:05.000Z","uid":90601,"like":95,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"11bc3d9a9c974491492f42aa2469591109790880","tid":1292492,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:50:04.000Z","msg":"有團體今日發起「九龍區大遊行」活動，並希望向附近大陸旅客宣揚反送中信息。有大陸旅客接受《立場新聞》訪問時明言不喜歡上街遊行的表達方式，但亦強調會把單張讀完，「都很想了解香港發生甚麼事」。<br />\n<br />\n今年26歲，來自內地西北的丹丹，今次是第一次來香港旅游。她從遊行人士手上接過解釋反送中運動的單張。丹丹表示，需要<span style=\"color: red;\">她不太喜歡這種上街遊行的表達方式，因比較吵鬧，「我未見過這樣的場面，心裡慌亂」。</span><br />\n<br />\n丹丹表示，她不了解為何今天有遊行，但<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">她一定會把單張讀完，「都很想了解香港發生甚麼事。」</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2XOBSXe\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2XOBSXe&d=ycfrXf17TK8Hvu747cBakUtrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=e87bb22b\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2XOBSXe</a><br />\n<br />\n林奠月娥：<br />\n<img src=\"https://vignette.wikia.nocookie.net/evchk/images/1/10/Wholefamdiethistime.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fvignette.wikia.nocookie.net%2Fevchk%2Fimages%2F1%2F10%2FWholefamdiethistime.png&h=c8e064c9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0858998732dcc0168785544f3fdec7a240770d06","tid":1292492,"uid":41343,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:51:33.000Z","msg":"佢哋睇完嘅結論會唔會係美國喺背後指使<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fd1fda0fa1b10a7d1f273ca167bd565ba09a644","tid":1292492,"uid":30063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:51:41.000Z","msg":"支共倒台會唔會逃犯條例就係導火線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996ab67540ce58b3d7c94ce140656d38cf6e61cc","tid":1292492,"uid":90601,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-07T10:54:25.000Z","msg":"我無野講"},{"pid":"72bee2a7bac6dae0c4d5794d29519aaba3e2456e","tid"